org.mapstruct.ap.internal.util.accessor

Interface Accessor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExecutableElementAccessor, VariableElementAccessor

    public interface Accessor
    This represents an Accessor that can be used for writing/reading a property to/from a bean.
    Author:
    Filip Hrisafov

      • getAccessedType

        TypeMirror getAccessedType()
        This returns the type that this accessor gives as a return. e.g. The ExecutableElement.getReturnType() if this is a method accessor, or Element.asType() for field accessors.
        Returns:
        the type that the accessor gives as a return
